Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.80,0:25:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H1F5CA5&}用導彈來張開彈幕 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}索瑪·皮麗斯啊
