Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.95,0:26:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}哪裏都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.18,0:26:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H8F4D3D&}再好好認真找
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.38,0:26:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}我在找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.30,0:26:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}那個是……
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.10,0:26:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H8F4D3D&}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.50,0:26:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}讓我報了之前的仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.50,0:26:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}還有算上布林格和迪梵的那一份
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.78,0:26:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}剎那 有兩顆隕石正在接近母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.90,0:26:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H8F4D3D&}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.70,0:27:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}戰鬥當中就別給我東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.40,0:27:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}不會吧 去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.79,0:27:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H8F4D3D&}滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.90,0:27:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.20,0:27:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}從隕石裏出現了MS的說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}我可不會再次中同一招數 拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.80,0:27:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}瞭解 導彈一起發射
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.90,0:27:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}不要啊
