Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.00,0:58:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}瞭解……瞭解……
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.30,0:58:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an8}（步槍單元原來是一次性裝備……真是浪費）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.40,0:58:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}這麼近的距離 你也用不到TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.00,0:58:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}已經發現維達了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.20,0:58:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}現在傳送給高達使者
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.10,0:58:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H612645&}幹得好 菲爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.66,0:59:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}這才是好戲登場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.10,0:59:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}我不會再被你打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.70,0:59:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H612645&}別來礙著我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.10,0:59:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}我們上 裏維夫
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.58,0:59:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}啊 TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.19,0:59:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H612645&}TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.70,0:59:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.00,0:59:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.60,1:00:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\3c&H131E3F&}我再殺你一次吧 誒 高達老兄
